         <OBJECT_CONTRACT>
            <TITLE>
               <P>Provision of Security and Stewarding Services</P>
            </TITLE>
            <REFERENCE_NUMBER>TT00064</REFERENCE_NUMBER>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="79713000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>The overall aim of this tender is to secure a relationship with a preferred supplier to provide Security and Stewarding related services as required for the venue’s busy programme of events.</P>
               <P>The objectives of the appointment of the preferred supplier includes:</P>
               <P>— To provide a professional, cost effective and quality service.</P>
               <P>— To provide a wide range of Security and Stewarding services.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">8500000.00</VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1">
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="79715000"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="79711000"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
               <n2016:NUTS CODE="UKD72"/>
               <MAIN_SITE>
                  <P>ACC Liverpool Site.</P>
               </MAIN_SITE>
               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>The Contractor shall provide Security services, which includes building security and concierge services, and Stewarding services on a call off basis for all internal and external areas of the Site in accordance with the standards detailed in this document.</P>
                  <P>The Contractor shall provide a professionally managed, high quality security, guarding service that has BS7858:2012 — Security screening of Individuals employed in a security environment and BS7499:2007 — Static guarding and mobile patrol or equivalent accreditation and complies with all legislation governing the security industry and Public Space Surveillance (CCTV).</P>
                  <P>The Contractor shall provide a professionally managed, high quality event stewarding service which complies with BS8406:2009 — Event Stewarding and Crowd Safety Services Code of Practice or equivalent accreditation.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
               <AC_PROCUREMENT_DOC/>
               <VAL_OBJECT CURRENCY="GBP">8500000.00</VAL_OBJECT>
               <DATE_START>2018-05-16</DATE_START>
               <DATE_END>2021-05-15</DATE_END>
               <RENEWAL/>
               <RENEWAL_DESCR>
                  <P>There is an option to extend for a further 2 years after the initial contract term.</P>
               </RENEWAL_DESCR>
               <NO_ACCEPTED_VARIANTS/>
               <NO_OPTIONS/>
               <NO_EU_PROGR_RELATED/>
